%h1 Projects

- @projects.each_slice(2) do |projects|
  %ul.thumbnails
    .row-fluid
      - projects.each do |project|
        = render partial: 'projects/project_thumb_large', locals: {project: project}


- content_for :left_sidebar do
  = render layout: '/shared/left_sidebar', locals: {title: 'Projects'} do
    %li= link_to 'New', new_project_path,  title: "Create a new project", data: {toggle: 'tooltip',  placement: 'right'}
